author: Ildefonso Ortiz and Brandon Darby, Ildefonso Ortiz and Brandon Darby
title: Mexico Reports 10 Percent Rise of Coronavirus Fatalities in Single Day
description: Mexican health officials confirmed a ten percent rise in fatalities tied to the novel coronavirus (COVID-19) in one day. The current death toll stands at 546 -- up 60 from the previous day.
